EXPERIMENTAL STATUS
This catalog is a personal experimental project. The author publishes
blocks that worked for her own video production. Code quality varies —
some blocks are polished, others are quick experiments saved because
they were useful. There is no promise of consistency, completeness, or
production-readiness across the catalog.

